{
  "stem": "12674.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm still absolutely, totally involved in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it never worked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was going to go back after I retired.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then when I retired, I realized that I didn't have the fire in the belly anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I didn't want to give it the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I would've been able to get into any school with my history, camps and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a child, I was hooked up on Egyptian-- on the old Egyptians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I love to read books about the pyramids, because I said my ancestors built them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took me until 1991 before I was able to see them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they did a good job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did a good job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was very, very fascinated, because the world around them was so primitive, especially Europe, you know, with bear skins and clubs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were doing all of these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was very fascinated by that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I always had a very, very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] inquisitive mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wanted to know how everything-- I wanted to know how it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And even if I didn't understand it, I wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And maybe four years later, if I could figure out how it worked out, very well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm still that way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Even if I don't know what it's like, I want to know what it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the childhood was very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a big mouth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want me to tell you one of my-- I want to give you an express-- a thing of what my father.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was a very religious man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I had said some of the things to my father that my children said to me-- and they were never disrespectful.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
